  "subject": "Dynamically determine image arch. and install GCC",
  "commit_message": "Dynamically determine image arch. and install GCC\n\nThe image architecture is currently hardcoded, this patch removes\nthat hardcoded value to allow for ARM64 builds to go through. It\nalso seems that GCC is not being installed and it is needed in\nthe image build process.\n\nChange-Id: I400c4a355cef80c3b60640500c8f7283b5bb3183\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-154\nSigned-off-by: Mohammed Naser <mnaser@vexxhost.com>\n",
